      <title>景顺表示，高等级债券利差可能进一步收窄</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/high-grade-bond-spreads-can-tighten-more-invesco-s-brill-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[景顺高级投资组合经理兼北美投资级信贷主管马特·布里尔 (Matt Brill) 表示，美国投资级公司债券利差已经接近历史低位，还有进一步收窄的空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/high-grade-bond-spreads-can-tighten-more-invesco-s-brill-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 18:29:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
